Class MovieInfo

  • Object
    • MovieInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class MovieInfo
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    Represents information of a movie Contains title, showing status, type, synopsis, directors, a list of casts, overallRating, a list of past reviews, base ticket price, rating, and sale about this movie
    Author:
    SSP2 Team1

      static class  MovieInfo.TypeOfMovie
